{"tid":1719300,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"TO公務員：唔好諗咁遠, 反左你老細先","createTime":"2019-11-14T05:12:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T10:52:11.000Z","uid":259321,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"890d273b81e40c1fecea56901086dc09cbc9f1a2","tid":1719300,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:12:29.000Z","msg":"認清一個事實<br />\n你同你老細雖然係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>同一部門</strong></span><br />\n佢係<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>既得利益者</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但你唔係呀！！！</strong></span><br />\n佢當你係乜？<br />\n高人工請返嚟<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>可以隨時被取代既condom</strong></span><br />\n所以你唔可以有相反意見<br />\n反左就898囉<br />\n<br />\n所以記住，要反某隔籬部門<br />\n首先要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">反左你老細先</strong><br />\n同埋要預左無左份工<ins></ins><br />\n一做就要做到底<br />\n<strong>[red]All or nothing</span></strong><br />\n可一不可再<br />\n唔好搞啲嘢唔嗲唔屌<br />\n<ins><ins><ins></ins></ins></ins>揚撚晒<br />\n無左份工又坐監呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c51223ee3a7dbc268a59d71fb3ead80bdd95b5a","tid":1719300,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:13:27.000Z","msg":"100"},{"pid":"5c1b9c14fe69bc2078fd8bad0f11d2d08911b2d8","tid":1719300,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:13:53.000Z","msg":"99"},{"pid":"4fadab284f8b28a73bb48711f76a9e985064ac0b","tid":1719300,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:14:43.000Z","msg":"98"},{"pid":"7a6da3d092a2d985ecb3000f9872b150d20372dd","tid":1719300,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:18:31.000Z","msg":"97"},{"pid":"e5d5cd057da49c5ffde3ef8e5f39434b85a76e10","tid":1719300,"uid":31076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep